# Circle USDC & Payment Processing
# Get from: https://console.circle.com/
CIRCLE_API_KEY=QVBJX0tFWV9your-circle-api-key-here
CIRCLE_ENTITY_SECRET=your-circle-entity-secret-here
NEXT_PUBLIC_CIRCLE_APP_ID=your-circle-app-id-here

# LayerZero V2 for cross-chain messaging
